I've successfully created a Graphviz visualization of the USDA agency structure based on your JSON data.

The resulting diagram shows:
- The United States Department of Agriculture (USDA) positioned on the left
- All 15 sub-agencies arranged to the right of USDA
- Directed edges showing that USDA "operates" each of its sub-agencies
- Clean, readable labels for all nodes

The visualization uses a left-to-right layout as requested, with USDA clearly positioned on the left and all other agencies spread out to the right. Each connection is labeled with "operates" to show the relationship between USDA and its various departments.
